<head><title>Leon Edwards</title></head>
<body><h1>Leon Edwards</h1>
    <hr />

<p>From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</p>

       <p><b>Leon Edwards</b> (born 25 August 1991) is a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_Jamaicans"target="_blank"> Jamaican-born English </a> professional<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts"target="_blank">l mixed martial artist. </a>He currently competes in the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Welterweight_(MMA)"target="_blank">Welterweight</a>division in the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship"target="_blank">Ultimate Fighting Championship</a>(UFC), where he is the current <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_UFC_champions#Welterweight_Championship"target="_blank">UFC Welterweight Champion.</a>A professional competitor since 2011,Edwards formerly competed for <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BAMMA"target="_blank"> BAMMA </a>Welterweight Champion. As of August 23, 2022, he is #6 in the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_current_UFC_fighters#Rankings"target="_blank"> UFC men pound-for-pound rankings. </a> <hr />

     
